Pachinko Lin (garfield@pacific.ice.ntnu.tw) wrote:
: Hello,

:    Could anyone recommend me a good book of information theory?

Cover and Thomas, "Elements of Information Theory." A recent book,
with nothing on crypto, but plenty on modern flavor things like
Kolmogorov complexity.

--Tim May

